    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>疾驰霓虹之路，驾驭无限魔法，塑造破碎世界。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《霓虹魔咒风暴》让你化身低科技赛博朋克世界中的强大法师，在崩塌的霓虹道路上疾奔。每一步都将你带向新敌人与宝藏，但别回头：道路会在你身后崩塌！用你的一切手段生存下去，劈开可破坏地形，释放毁灭性法术，创造每次冒险独特的疯狂协同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/cc5d84582b008f5590fa9a33115359f6.poster.avif?t=1754909091\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/cc5d84582b008f5590fa9a33115359f6.webm?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/cc5d84582b008f5590fa9a33115359f6.mp4?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>脚下崩塌的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境本身成为障碍，地形在你身后崩塌，法术与敌人碰撞时四分五裂。每一次冒险都挑战你保持领先，每个决定都将你推向未知更深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/f5a8bbd864d28fd2d573f0a9f3b4b4bc.poster.avif?t=1754909091\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/f5a8bbd864d28fd2d573f0a9f3b4b4bc.webm?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/f5a8bbd864d28fd2d573f0a9f3b4b4bc.mp4?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无限协同与升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用为疯狂连招而设计的法术系统，打造属于你的魔法风格。叠加、升级和强化法术，创造难以想象的力量。尝试能触发额外法术的回响施法、成倍放大范围与冲击的巨兽施法，以及在战场上释放混乱的辅助效果。每一件装备、印记和饰品都能让你的法师更强大，一次施法即可消灭整波敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/c2e218cfc7e82dbf0cca04d0f11fcc2f.poster.avif?t=1754909091\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/c2e218cfc7e82dbf0cca04d0f11fcc2f.webm?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298080/extras/c2e218cfc7e82dbf0cca04d0f11fcc2f.mp4?t=1754909091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过霓虹核心实现永久进度</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你深入霓虹世界，你将获得元货币——能量球、星星、宝石和霓虹——用于在霓虹核心解锁永久升级。投资新法术、能力和特质，扩展你的武器库，并提升风暴等级以解锁更高难度挑战和新敌人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的道路，你的选择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都可选择你的策略。出发前配置你的法师：选择法术、命运、原型和印记，匹配你的风格。在冒险过程中，适应分支路径，决定是探索每个区域以获取最大奖励，还是直奔最终Boss。每一个选择都会影响你的进度和法师的成长。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>低科技赛博朋克世界中的破坏性魔法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入这个被霓虹浸染、充满异界生物和几何地貌的世界。在《霓虹魔咒风暴》中，法术会重塑地形，施法时碎片飞溅，像素艺术与3D物理碰撞，带来爆炸性沉浸体验。鲜艳色彩与极简赛博朋克美学让每一次遭遇都既惊艳又致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你准备好拥抱霓虹，释放前所未有的魔法了吗？道路已在等待，但它不会停留太久……</strong></p>",
